    <abstract id="aspace_e24d65b7a7a569e396e1712432686499">Adelphi Academy is a private preparatory school founded in 1863 by Dr. Edward S. Bunker and Aaron Chadwick. This collection documents the development and evolution of the Academy's curriculum, its physical growth and infrastructural development in its early years, and student life. It also documents Adelphi College prior to its becoming Adelphi University in 1963.</abstract>
